{"tid":1653743,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"推去國際！FreeHongKong 手勢","createTime":"2019-10-14T08:26:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-15T10:52:42.000Z","uid":269088,"like":3,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"11db6ccd0aa33e9164896bb8613d41f900a88664","tid":1653743,"uid":269088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T08:26:50.000Z","msg":"之前 #eye4HK 有遮眼 profile，好多人用影自拍就可以表態，但所關注係集中黑警開鎗射中女義士眼單一事件。<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">但可以睇到一個手勢晌國際文宣係好重要！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n見呢排 NBA 事件好多外國人關注，仲特登籌款印 T 去宣示 Stand with Hong Kong，但<span style=\"color: blue;\">如果無 T 無標語啲人根本好難 make 到 noise</span>（同時無可能每場都派 T），<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">所以有一個手勢就可以令到即使無標語道具都可以用畫面對 Free Hong Kong 表示支持！</span></span>尤其是騰訊好誠實咁又播番 NBA，如果鏡頭影住觀眾用同一手勢去支持 Free Hong Kong 應該係好好嘅宣示方法！<span style=\"color: blue;\">同時可以伸延去其他公眾直播賽事場合。</span><br />\n另外亦都<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">方便其他外國組織影相時做手勢作出支持</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sVz3mVF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsVz3mVF.png&h=a214fa2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢個係建議嘅手勢，手背向外，有 &quot;F&quot;ree / &quot;3&quot; Three，形態亦似 K 字。<br />\n暫時未搵到有無撞其他手勢意思（包括手語會唔會有其他 meaning），唔知有無手足可以 check 到。<br />\nP 牌仔推唔到"},{"pid":"af429e908604929b5946abf8af6dd17a2d538880","tid":1653743,"uid":67332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T08:27:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d31a6a340bccdcb75be49e7aaa1b37b7459ad23e","tid":1653743,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T08:46:08.000Z","msg":"就咁🙋&zwj;♂️會唔會易d？ 又用開"},{"pid":"3257b8b7936dae485cf89fbaa2c1393f76af1bdc","tid":1653743,"uid":34503,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d31a6a340bccdcb75be49e7aaa1b37b7459ad23e","tid":1653743,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T08:46:08.000Z","msg":"就咁🙋&zwj;♂️會唔